<HEADLINE>
MINE EYES HAVE SEEN THE COMING OF A LOT OF WACKY STUFF 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(Eds: Passages in italics are indicated by ``Begin italics'' and
``End italics.'') 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For use by special arrangement
only. Asian and European points: Call Karl Horwitz in Paris for
