   (Begin italics)Tenting on the ol' re-enactment campground
apparently can get mighty lonesome. So the Camp Chase Gazette also
runs personal ads:(End italics)
</P>
<P>
   SWM, 43, C.S.A., Officer ... is looking for his Southern Angel
who would enjoy being in a long-term relationship, possible
