</P>
<P>
   Chinese leaders are gambling that even as political relations
with the United States go through the grinder, Western trade and
investment will continue unaffected.
</P>
<P>
   ``Capital and technology are now beyond political control,''
Zhang said. ``As long as the social situation here is stable and
the economy is open, capital will come.''
</P>
