<HEADLINE>
GOATS ON TRIAL AS URBAN WEED KILLERS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (repeating to add photo note)  
 (ATTN: Mont., Wyo., Calif.)  (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(DW) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
