the former Boston Red Sox pitching hero from Cuba who won 229
major-league games. The second-year baseball coach at Savannah
College of Art and Design has been reunited with his son, who quit
his job in Miami to work as his father's assistant. ``Family is
everything,'' the elder Tiant said. ``It is even more important
than baseball.'' (Curtright, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
